Shahid's sister Sanah engaged to actor Mayank Pahwa: Report.
Shahid Kapoor's little sister Sanah Kapoor is set to get hitched, if a report in Pinkvilla is to be believed.Reportedly, Sanah, who made her debut with brother Shahid and dad Pankaj Kapur in Shaandaar, got engaged to Mayank Pahwa, who is the son of actor Manoj Pahwa and Seema Bhargava Pahwa, earlier this month.ALSO READ: Mira gets irritated when I call her Bhabhi, says Shahid's sister Sanah Kapoor ALSO READ: Shahid and Mira go on a date sans Misha 